Name: p
Description: the prime factor p of n

Name: qInv

Name: r_i
Description: a prime factor r_i of n, where i >= 3

Name: t_i
Description:
the CRT coefficient t_i = (r_1 * r_2 * ... *
        r_(i-1))^(-1) mod r_i

Name: pub
Description: Public key for HSS/LMS hash-based digital signature
